            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Vario Clementi <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>provinciarum Belgicae <lb n="3"/>Germaniae superioris Germaniae <lb n="4"/>inferioris Raetiae Mauretaniae Caesar<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>ens</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Lusitaniae Ciliciae <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>al</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>miliar</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> auxiliorum in Mauretaniam Tingitanam ex <lb n="7"/>Hispania misso<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>um <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>al</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uno</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itum</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>lpiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ictricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> II Gallorum Macedonicae <lb n="9"/>cives Romani ex Italia et aliis provinciis <lb n="10"/>in Raetia consistentes
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nach 156/157 n. Chr., als der Geehrte Prokurator in Raetia war, und vor dessen Amtsantritt als ab epistulis Augustorum um 162-165 n. Chr.</p>
